Metformin in adults with type 1 diabetes: Design and methods of REducing with 
MetfOrmin Vascular Adverse Lesions (REMOVAL): An international multicentre 
trial.

Petrie JR(1), Chaturvedi N(2), Ford I(1), Hramiak I(3), Hughes AD(1), Jenkins 
