Linear-In-The-Parameters Oblique Least Squares (LOLS) Provides More Accurate 
Estimates of Density-Dependent Survival.

Vieira VM(1), Engelen AH(2), Huanel OR(3), Guillemin ML(3)(4).

Author information:
(1)MARETEC, Instituto Superior Técnico, Universidade Técnica de Lisboa, Av. 
