Follow-Up of Alcohol Consumption After Liver Transplantation: Interest of an 
Addiction Team?

Donnadieu-Rigole H(1)(2), Olive L(1), Nalpas B(3)(4), Winter A(5), Ursic-Bedoya 
J(6), Faure S(6), Pageaux GP(6)(7), Perney P(3)(7).

Author information:
(1)Department of Addictology, Saint-Eloi Hospital, CHRU Montpellier, 
Montpellier, France.
(2)INSERM, U1183, IRMB, Saint-Eloi Hospital, CHU Montpellier, Montpellier, 
