Discovery of Mycobacterium tuberculosis InhA Inhibitors by Binding Sites 
Comparison and Ligands Prediction.

Štular T(1), Lešnik S(1), Rožman K(2), Schink J(3), Zdouc M(3), Ghysels A(4), 
