Long-term exposure to urban air pollution and the relationship with life 
expectancy in cohort of 3.5 million people in Silesia.

Dziubanek G(1), Spychała A(2), Marchwińska-Wyrwał E(3), Rusin M(4), Hajok I(5), 
Ćwieląg-Drabek M(6), Piekut A(7).

